ZH: 这本书有一千页。
EN: This book has one thousand pages.

ZH: 昨天我花了一千块钱买了新手机。
EN: Yesterday I spent one thousand RMB on a new phone.

ZH: 他在一千米的高山上建了一座房子。
EN: He built a house on a mountain one thousand meters high.

ZH: 我们公司有一千名员工。
EN: Our company has one thousand employees.

ZH: 他每天跑一千米。
EN: He runs one kilometer every day.

ZH: 那个村庄有一千户人家。
EN: That village has one thousand households.

ZH: 这是我一千次尝试后的成果。
EN: This is the result of my one thousandth attempt.

ZH: 她花了一千个小时学会了弹钢琴。
EN: She spent one thousand hours learning to play the piano.

ZH: 我们计划在一千天内完成这项工程。
EN: We plan to complete this project within one thousand days.

ZH: 半千年前，这里是一片繁荣的城市。
EN: Five hundred years ago, this was a thriving city.

ZH: 这幅画值千金。
EN: This painting is worth a thousand pieces of gold.

ZH: 他一千次告诉过我不要这么做。
EN: He has told me a thousand times not to do that.

ZH: 这个问题已经困扰我千年。
EN: This problem has haunted me for centuries.

ZH: 一千克等于一吨。
EN: One thousand kilograms is equal to one ton.

ZH: 他独自徒步穿越了一千公里的沙漠。
EN: He crossed a thousand kilometers of desert on foot alone.

ZH: 他接触过的人数已经超过一千。
EN: The number of people he has interacted with has exceeded one thousand.

ZH: 他用了一千盎司黄金买下了这幢房子。
EN: He used a thousand ounces of gold to buy this house.

ZH: 这片土地已经被开垦了千年。
EN: This land has been cultivated for a thousand years.

ZH: 这个古城已有千年的历史。
EN: This ancient city has a history of a thousand years.

ZH: 我们游览了有千年历史的古寺。
EN: We visited an ancient temple with a history of a thousand years.
